			<h3>About Us</h3>
			<p>Stud & Found is an online community for people who want to buy or sell their single earrings. We match your lonesome earrings to their soul mates – A Romeo for your Juliet, a Lancelot to your Guinever – and give you the opportunity to sell your single earrings back to the community so they can find a new home.</p>
			<h3>Our Manifesto</h3>
			<p>Star-crossed lovers only exist in fiction. We find matches.</p>
			<h3>How it works</h3>
			<p>
				1. Locate your single earrings. They might be hidden in your jewelry box, in your back jean pockets, on an earring rack.<br>
				2. Find your earring based on brand, material, color and size.<br>
				3. Decide if you want to buy a match, or sell it for cash at the current buying and selling prices.<br>
				4. Ship or wait for shipping!<br>
					a. If you decide to sell your earring, we will send you a prepaid padded mailing envelope. Or you can print out the label at home and package it in a padded envelope or wrapped with tissue.<br>
